flowchart TD
    Input[Entity Produces Output] --> Checker[Checker/Validator Runs]
    Checker --> Eval{Check Results}
    Eval -- "PASSED / INFO only" --> Accept[Output Accepted]
    
    Eval -- "BLOCKER / WARNING" --> IssueCountCheck{Issue Count Decreased?}
    IssueCountCheck -- No --> Escalate[Escalate to User: Stalled]
    IssueCountCheck -- Yes --> IterationCheck{Iteration > 3?}
    
    IterationCheck -- Yes --> AskUser[Prompt User Override]
    AskUser -- "Proceed Anyway" --> Accept
    AskUser -- "Adjust Approach" --> UserInput[Discuss New Approach]
    
    IterationCheck -- No --> ReSpawn[Re-spawn Entity with Check Results Inlined]
    ReSpawn --> Checker
